From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude.ai.2026@simonlaux.de>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 16:56:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 57/64] web-app: move Experimental features to their own
 settings section

Advanced had grown into a grab bag: log, server, multi-device, the
whole experimental block, analytics, autostart. Experimental features
now get their own entry in the settings navigation (using the shipped
but previously unreferenced test-tube icon), and Advanced keeps the
rest. The location-streaming info dialog's pointer is updated to
'Settings / Experimental features'.
