 .../frontend/src/components/Settings/Advanced.tsx     |  6 ------
 .../src/components/Settings/ExperimentalFeatures.tsx  |  2 +-
 .../frontend/src/components/Settings/Settings.tsx     | 11 +++++++++++
 4 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

